 \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;line-height:20px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">第二节 国家863项目组织实施模式的实践&nbsp;</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:Arial, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;line-height:20px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">第三节 社会公益性科技项目组织实施模式的实践</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:Arial, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:20px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\"><br />\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:Arial, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;line-height:20px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">第八章 科技项目成果管理&nbsp;</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:Arial, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:20px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\"><br />\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:Arial, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;line-height:20px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">第一节 科技计划项目成果管理&nbsp;</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:Arial, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;line-h